SIGNATURE DbmAccess

-- Access mode for Simple Data Base Manager 
-- Version 1.0

-- this provides the access mode for Dbm as a non-parameterized type

TYPE access == reader writer tryReader tryWriter
    -- kind of access to data base. N readers or 1 writer are
    -- allowed at the same time, never both.
    -- with the try forms, an access acquiring operation
    -- immediatly fails if the access is not granted.
